Honestly this type of error is tricky and it could be happening for multiple reasons (*for example, having the runner, steps or features outside the test folder*), however, based in the info you shared, try adding the name of the feature file in the path:


    @RunWith(CucumberWithSerenity.class)
    @CucumberOptions(features = &quot;src/test/resources/features/yourfile.feature&quot;,
            glue = &quot;stepdefinitions&quot;)

In case you have a directory inside the step definition folder, you must do:


    @RunWith(CucumberWithSerenity.class)
    @CucumberOptions(features = &quot;src/test/resources/features/yourfile.feature&quot;,
                glue = &quot;stepdefinitions/your_directory&quot;)

